==Natural hybrids==

The following natural [[hybrid]]s involving ''N. inermis'' have been recorded.

*''[[Nepenthes bongso|N. bongso]]'' × ''N. inermis'' 
*''N. inermis'' × ''[[Nepenthes singalana|N. singalana]]''
*''N. inermis'' × ''[[Nepenthes spathulata|N. spathulata]]''<ref name=Clarke />
*''N. inermis'' × ''[[Nepenthes talangensis|N. talangensis]]'' [=''[[Nepenthes x pyriformis|N. × pyriformis]]'']<ref name=Clarke />

